ews/willy-wonka-experience-uk-glasgow-scam-b2504130.html?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR0HyEbWmI8mvRDeO-NbrWw7odEUQ6uUa93w9kJnt5_YwBwBPeakPjtm3yA#Echobox=1709158821">科斯蒂·帕特森 (Kirsty Paterson) 此前曾公开讲述了这次灾难性的经历</a>，并透露她尚未收到为演出提供的 500 英镑报酬。</p><p> “整件事简直就是一团糟。老实说，这令人震惊，”她告诉<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-13131605/willy-wonka-scam-embarrassed-actress-memorise-ai-script-not-paid.html"><i>《每日邮报》</i></a> 。</p><p>后来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/willys-chocolate-factory-experience-wonka-actor-speaks-out-about-dangerous-and-heartbreaking-event-3594918">被雇来模仿威利·旺卡的演员之一保罗·康奈尔透露了更多有关灾难性事件如何发生的信息。</a> “剧本是由人工智能生成的 15 页胡言乱语，我只是在独白这些疯狂的事情，”他告诉<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/willy-wonka-experience-glasgow-chocolate-event-b2504464.html"><i>《独立报》</i></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sydney-sweeney-mocks-glasgows-wonka-experience-in-snl-skit-3596176">西德尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 最近在<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目中表演小品时也对这一活动进行了取笑</a>。</p><p><i>威利·旺卡：震惊英国的丑闻</i>将于 3 月 16 日在第五频道播出。</p><p>即将 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/willy-wonka-experience-documentary-to-air-on-channel-5-3598154">在第五频道播出的《威利旺卡体验》纪录片</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ;
